  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XLIX 7
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Belief in the Unseen
---
Allâh hath endeared the faith to you and hath made it beautiful in
your hearts, and hath made hateful unto you disbelief and lewdness and
rebellion. Such are they who are the rightly guided.
